distribution.name: Additional_file_S3.1.xls
distribution.description: Highly significant SNPs (genome-wise FDR ≤ 5 %, FDR ≤ 1% and genome-wise Bonferroni ≤ 5 %) resulting from GWAS using single SNP regression mixed linear model for milk production (MILK), fat production (FAT), fat deviation (FATD), protein production (PROT) and protein deviation (PROTD).
